  "text": "We expect that this work and EPIPOX will be instrumental in developing safer smallpox vaccines and thereby in preventing zoonosis caused by other orthopoxviruses, including MPXV, which is also a potential terrorist bioweapon. In the future, we plan to enhance EPIPOX with validated and/or experimentally determined epitopes, upgrade protein annotations with functional information, and include additional features such as TAP transport [CITATION_1] , ERAAP cleavage [CITATION_2] , and T-cell epitope immunodominance. In sum, we would expect EPIPOX to establish itself as a facilitating resource of true utility in inter alia immunoinformatic characterization of viral genomics and computational reverse vaccinology.",
